{"id":245877,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-紧急关注：维权人士朱承志被以煽动颠/","date":"2012-08-09T06:16:46Z","modified":"2012-08-09T06:16:46Z","title":"维权网 | 紧急关注：维权人士朱承志被以“煽动颠覆国家政权罪”逮捕（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员子夕报道）湖南维权人士 朱承志 先生行政拘留期满被邵阳警方转押到看守所</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>余天后，本网辗转收到邵阳警方对他的逮捕通知书。逮捕通知书的日期是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，罪名是“煽动颠覆国家政权罪”，目前 朱承志 先生被羁押在邵阳市看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，出狱不久的民运斗士李旺阳“绳索绕颈”离奇辞世后，引起社会各界的强烈震惊和质疑，作为李旺阳的生前好友，朱承志先生因关注李旺阳死因和安抚家属，受到警方的威胁，因拒不写不再关注李旺阳死因的保证书而被以“扰乱社会治安”行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>拘留期满后被邵阳警方以“问题还没有调查清楚”为由直接关押到看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>多年来， 朱承志 先生努力践行一个公民的社会责任，福州三网友案、北京倪玉兰案庭审、王荔蕻案庭审、祭奠民主先驱林昭墓，等等， 朱承志 先生都身体力行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另一位湖南维权人士肖勇，因关注李旺阳事件于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>被邵阳警方劳教一年半。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9VDtCNQKGe8/UCMpDHIAnAI/AAAAAAAALHg/8g50CCKLYJk/s1600/%E6%9C%B1%E6%89%BF%E5%BF%97%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E7%A6%8F%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9VDtCNQKGe8/UCMpDHIAnAI/AAAAAAAALHg/8g50CCKLYJk/s320/%E6%9C%B1%E6%89%BF%E5%BF%97%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E7%A6%8F%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B.jpg\" width=\"212\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>朱承志声援福州三网友</span> </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CRTs1lYd-Lc/UCMpIPKVeTI/AAAAAAAALHo/wZSuMIH22x8/s1600/%E8%80%81%E6%9C%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"310\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CRTs1lYd-Lc/UCMpIPKVeTI/AAAAAAAALHo/wZSuMIH22x8/s320/%E8%80%81%E6%9C%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>三网友之一的吴华英呼唤朱承志回家</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kP85tuaDmyE/UCMpRnEnELI/AAAAAAAALHw/bbEDiae4hyc/s1600/%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F0845.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kP85tuaDmyE/UCMpRnEnELI/AAAAAAAALHw/bbEDiae4hyc/s320/%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F0845.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>朱承志的逮捕通知书</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7160921693044324451?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}